I need to get involved too.

00:23:35.870 --> 00:23:37.820 align:middle line:84%
I need to help out
more, whether that

00:23:37.820 --> 00:23:40.080 align:middle line:84%
was at home, or in their
community, or at work.

00:23:40.080 --> 00:23:41.380 align:middle line:84%
And the second
thing that happened

00:23:41.380 --> 00:23:44.670 align:middle line:84%
was that an antibody in
the saliva increased,

00:23:44.670 --> 00:23:46.240 align:middle line:90%
came to the fore right away.

00:23:46.240 --> 00:23:49.780 align:middle line:84%
And that antibody is very
significant, because it

00:23:49.780 --> 00:23:50.930 align:middle line:90%
increases the immune system.

