00:25:12.560 --> 00:25:15.180 align:middle line:84%
One of the difficulties
in the way in which we live

00:25:15.180 --> 00:25:19.730 align:middle line:84%
in the world today with the huge
population we're dealing with,

00:25:19.730 --> 00:25:22.550 align:middle line:84%
and the bills that
we have piling up,

00:25:22.550 --> 00:25:26.080 align:middle line:84%
and the family problems,
and the mother-in-law,

00:25:26.080 --> 00:25:29.290 align:middle line:84%
and all of the difficulties
that we're dealing with,

00:25:29.290 --> 00:25:31.800 align:middle line:84%
is we stop feeling
grateful as to what's

00:25:31.800 --> 00:25:35.390 align:middle line:84%
actually good in our
lives, and we start

00:25:35.390 --> 00:25:37.950 align:middle line:90%
