our immune system.

00:25:49.230 --> 00:25:51.550 align:middle line:84%
People who enjoy many
positive emotions,

00:25:51.550 --> 00:25:54.380 align:middle line:84%
who are more optimistic,
actually live longer.

00:25:54.380 --> 00:25:56.350 align:middle line:84%
So when we do an
act of kindness,

00:25:56.350 --> 00:25:59.400 align:middle line:84%
when we commit an act of
kindness, when we help another

00:25:59.400 --> 00:26:01.570 align:middle line:84%
and we feel better
about it, we're actually

00:26:01.570 --> 00:26:04.500 align:middle line:84%
